    <section id="tweet">
      <h2>Tweet this week</h2>
      <p>Auto-generated tweet from this week's top insight:</p>
      <div class="tweet-box">
        <pre class="tweet-text">The MCP top 10 just reshuffled hard.

@PrefectHQ/fastmcp: #7 → #1
CoplayDev/unity-mcp: #1 → #20

Freshness beats stars. Repos that stopped shipping paid the price.

Full breakdown: agentrank-ai.com/blog/this-week-in-mcp-2026-03-24/</pre>
